From: Hermes Project <hermes@local>
Date: Fri, 11 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] glslang: add missing <cstdint> include for GCC 15 compat

GCC 15 removed implicit inclusion of <cstdint> types. SpvBuilder.h uses
uint32_t without including <cstdint>, causing build failures on GCC 15+.

--- a/src/3rdparty/glslang/SPIRV/SpvBuilder.h
+++ b/src/3rdparty/glslang/SPIRV/SpvBuilder.h
@@ -61,6 +61,7 @@
 #include <set>
 #include <sstream>
 #include <stack>
+#include <cstdint>
 #include <unordered_map>
 #include <map>

